listitem.para:
To store certificates, either use the Barbican &ostack;
service, a local directory (Local), or the Magnum
Database (x590keypair).

sect1.para:
The &o_container; &barcl; consists of the following roles:
   magnum-server. It can either be deployed on a &contrnode;
   or on a cluster—see .
   When deploying the role onto a &contrnode;, additional RAM is required for the
   &o_container; server. It is recommended to only deploy the role to a &contrnode;
   that has 16 GB RAM.
